platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: With its gorgeous photos and step-by-step instructions, this compilation of more than 15,000 recipes from The New York Times vaults belongs in every kitchen. We love how easy it is to save and search for recipes, and themed collections like Easy Cakes, Beer Cocktails, and A Taste of New Orleans are a mouthwatering delight. The app also features dozens of short instructional videos on topics like trussing chicken and julienning peppersperfect for novice chefs eager to dive in and start cooking.
